Description: Peat-node telemetry pusher for Raspberry Pi nodes
 Pushes system telemetry to a local peat-node instance via the
 PeatSidecar HTTP/gRPC API. Intended to run as a systemd service
 alongside peat-node on Raspberry Pi field nodes.
